      "content": "that makes sense. so when i'm writing the section on meritocracy, should i present it as a valid philosophical position that just has some flaws, or should i frame it more like a way for people to ignore the reality of systemic racism? i want to know if there's a way to describe their stance that shows it might be fundamentally disconnected from how society actually works.",
